quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  4,1,"EEHEY mon yim…ďe! Kulee Joomi mon On Tak…óo on immorde e woŇčkii goooti, O Tagi immorde e makki debbo makki, O Saaki immorde e …ďen …ói…óo wor…ďe …óuu…óu…ďe e rew…ďe. KUlee Alla On Mo naamnanirton sabu mun, [rento…óon kadi] e en…óammaaje …óen. Pellet, Alla Laatike e dow mon Deenoowo."
  4,2,"Jonne wondu…ďe …ďen jaw…óeele ma…ď…ďe …óen. Wata on waostondir so…ďe …óen ko laa…ďi. Wata on √Īaamu jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen [wa…óton …óum] e jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen. Pellet, …óum laatike bakkaatu maw…óo."
  4,3,"Si on kulii roŇčkugol nun…óude e wondu…ďe …ďen, ndeesee ko laa…ďani on e rew…ďe, …ói…óo e tato e nayo. Si on kulii roŇčkugol nun…óude, wa…óee gooto maa …ďe jeyru…óon √Īaame mon ; ko …óum …ďuri …ďa…ótaade nde on too√Īu."
  4,4,"Jonniree rew…ďe …ďen teŇče ma…ď…ďe …óen dokkal. Si …ďe anniyanike on go…ó…óum e …óen [teŇče] e hoore laa…ďal woŇčkii, √Īaamee …óum, no newanii on …ďuu…ďani on."
  4,5,"Wata on jonnitu …óay…ďe …ďe jaw…óele mon …óen …óe Alla Wa…óirani on dartor…óe. √Ďamminee …ďe e majje, koltinon …ďe, wowlanon …ďe konngol mo∆ī∆īol."
  4,6,"Njarribee wondu…ďe …ďen si …ďe yottike desal, si on so'ii e ma…ď…ďe peewal, njonnitee…ďe jaw…óeele ma…ďe …óen, wata on √Īaamir …óe faŇčtinngol e he…óoo yo …ďe mawnude. On taw…óo ko o galo, yo o naŇčto, on taw…óo ko o baaso, yo o √Īaamir no mo∆ī∆īiri. Si on jonnitii…ďe jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen, seedinee e dow ma…ď…ďe. Alla Yonii Hasboowo."